nodes.text: The hunanetre, or huna-netre, were a type of creature that could be found on Rentalles. While on display at a celebration of the Outer Rim on Serenno, the Dianectric Menagerie contained a number of hunanetre. Dagra Van, the beastmaster of Crakka the Hutt, captured a hunanetre on Rentalles, which Crakka presented to Jabba Desilijic Tiure as a gift.
